profile_positions.description:
Location: 's-Hertogenbosch (NL)

Key Roles and Responsibilities:
• Develop and steward annual sales plan (area: Benelux, Scandinavia, Germany, Switzerland, Austria, Ireland and United Kingdom) and monthly sales updates from a volume and Average Gross Margin perspective;
• Support area Sales Reps in negotiation, deal meeting and relationship development;
• Support Customer Service Representatives during their daily activities;
• Manage pricing, discounts and rebates within guidelines;
• Implement customer service level differentiation program;
• Collate customer, market and industry data’s as well as sales demand and demand changes.

Location: 's-Hertogenbosch (NL)

Key Roles and Responsibilities:
• Develop and manage a customer account plan for Unilever and Amcor Flexibles;
• Develop an evolving value creating customer alliance at each account;
• Negotiate within guidelines prices, discounts, rebates and sales terms to optimise profitability;
• Conduct sales calls and customer visits to develop sales;

Location: Luxembourg (L)

Key Roles and Responsibilities:
• Volume, turnover and profitability of the product group Coated OPP films in the area Europe, Africa, Middle East, Asia and Oceania;
• Product group, communication and promotion strategy;
• New product and applications developments;
• Competition intelligence;
